---
title: Lebanese Lamb Koftas with Quinoa & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Plate up dinner tonight with this fragrant, Middle Eastern signature dish. These juicy koftas are packed with a flavourful, mild spice blend and a delicate bite from the hidden pine nuts. With a finishing drizzle of zesty yoghurt, we rate this mouth-watering meal 4/4 koftas!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lebanese-lamb-koftas-be8c953e.jpg
